					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Speak With Dead dialogue for Gortash's mother, Sally Flymm. Gortash tadpoled his parents, who sold him into slavery in his youth. They were aware of their state but cannot resist the tadpole's compulsion - which made them appear to be huge fans of their son. When they die, the tadpole loses its grip over them."
				}
